OL,3,CMartyn's Law laid before parliament
OL,5,FRequirements at 'standard tier'
OL,6,Finclude training staff on "simple and
OL,7,Flow cost" procedures like identifying
OL,8,Fsafe exit routes and locking doors and
OL,9,Fwindows.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, 'enhanced tier' premises
OL,12,Fwill be required to undertake
OL,13,Fadditional steps to reduce the
OL,14,Fvulnerability of the premises to
OL,15,Fterrorist attacks.
