OL,3,CMartyn's Law laid before parliament
OL,5,FMichael Kill, CEO of the Night Time
OL,6,FIndustries Association, commended
OL,7,FFigen "for her relentless advocacy in
OL,8,Fhonour of her son" but added there
OL,9,Fwere "challenges" that lie ahead.
OL,11,FMr kill said: "Martyn's Law aims to
OL,12,Fbolster safety measures at publicly
OL,13,Faccessible venues, a goal we
OL,14,Fwholeheartedly support.
OL,16,F"However, as we advance, it is crucial
OL,17,Fto address the proportionality of the
OL,18,Fproposed measures, within all settings.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
