OL,3,CMartyn's Law laid before parliament
OL,5,F"We must ensure that the balance
OL,6,Fbetween heightened security and
OL,7,Fpractical implementation is carefully
OL,8,Fconsidered.
OL,10,F"Key concerns include the operational
OL,11,Fimpact, skill set required of venue
OL,12,Foperators and the financial
OL,13,Fimplications of enforcing these new
OL,14,Fsafety protocols.
OL,16,F"While the objectives of Martyn's Law
OL,17,Fare commendable, it is essential that
OL,18,Fthe legislation is designed with
OL,19,Ffeasibility and fairness in mind.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
